question: Scientists find dinosaur fossils in the bottom rock layers of a cliff and mammal fossils in the middle rock layer of the cliff. Which could best be concluded from this evidence?
candidate_answers: (A) Dinosaurs ate plants. (B) Dinosaurs were eaten by the mammals. (C) Dinosaurs lived on Earth before the mammals. (D) Dinosaurs and mammals lived at the same time.
answer: Dinosaurs lived on Earth before the mammals.
label: C
